<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />過新年的時候，<delay8 />
待在家裡悠閒地玩歌牌<delay8 />
感覺也不錯耶～<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是，<delay20 />
我一個人要<delay8 />同時<delay8 />讀牌跟搶牌，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實還滿忙的耶～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00">所謂「新年初夢」，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是指<delay8 />今天晚上做的夢，對吧～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />我好期待喔～<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了夢到好吃的夢，<delay20 />
我要在枕頭下面<delay20 />
放進<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />的照片睡覺喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00">除了<delay8 />過年的時候，<delay20 />
我不太吃年糕耶～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這是為什麼呢～？<pageBreak /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想到了！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可能是因為我在過年的時候，<delay8 />
就把一年份的年糕吃光光了喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00">我打算用毛筆寫下<delay8 />
新年新希望<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />可是<delay8 />當我回過神來，<delay20 />卻發現上面寫著<delay8 />
「<tag a="135" b="3" arg="0xcd00" />」、「<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />」<delay20 />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之類的食物啊～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣看來，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的新年新希望<delay8 />只會是<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「成為島上最貪吃的人！」了吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00">說到日本的新年，<delay20 />
果然<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是不能忘記壓歲錢！<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要用媽媽給我的壓歲錢<delay20 />
買什麼好呢～<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等下去<colour id="3" />豆狸<colour id="65535" />那邊<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />逛一下好了～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>